Suicide Prevention Through Education - See A New Sun Foundation Inc. Home About SANS Resources In Memoriam Contact Donate Press Releases Gala for Hope Take a Depression Screening For most people, suicide is a subject too uncomfortable to discuss. Add the "it won't happen to anyone close to me" factor, and it's no wonder that suicide is largely ignored as a leading cause of death in the U.S. According to the U.S.A Suicide: 2014 Official Final Data report, every 30 seconds somebody attempts suicide. Every 12.3 minutes somebody dies by suicide. Deaths from suicide are preventable. Recognizing the often subtle danger signs from a friend or family member in trouble is important, and taking immediate and appropriate action is key. But few people know the signs, what to do about it, or where to find help. The See A New Sun Foundation aims to prevent suicide through education and early intervention. See A New Sun Foundation was honored to be able to present the following three awards in 2022: ​ ​ Westford : Andrew P. Walker Memorial Award - Presented to James Peterson Littleton : Bryan Whitcomb Memorial Award - Presented to Isabella Anderson Groton : Gina Duffy Silva Award - Presented to Kyle Bowman​ Congratulations to the recipients! Absolutely SANCS mission is to take great love to hopeless Chinese peasant orphan children by providing loving homes, clothing, food, education and medical care. Since 1996 we have been caring for desperate orphan children. Newsweek, the Chinese government and the media have recognized our work. SANCS is a non-denominational tax-deductible 501(C)(3) . SANCS is an organization that was formed in 1994 and is supported entirely by family, friends and churches of many beliefs. All donations are used for the support of the children. The mothers and our Chinese office manager receive a salary; Jane and all the other staff are self-supporting volunteers. SANCS is an acronym for Sino-American Nonprofit Cooperative Services which means China and America cooperating together to serve the people for no profit. “ Pure and Lasting religion in the sight of God our Father means that we must care for orphans in their troubles.” James 1:27 SANCS 913-259-8003 © 2025 SANCS

FBI Insights: Exploring the World of Cybersecurity The Rise of Cybercrime: Understanding the Threats We Face The FBI has been at the forefront of combating cybercrime, and it's essential to understand the scope of this issue. In recent years, cyberattacks have become increasingly sophisticated, with hackers targeting individuals, businesses, and governments alike. The consequences are severe, resulting in financial losses, compromised personal data, and even national security threats. The FBI has seen a significant increase in reported cybercrimes, with many cases going unreported due to the fear of reputational damage or lack of awareness about how to report these incidents. It's crucial for individuals and organizations to take proactive measures to protect themselves from these attacks. FBI's Efforts to Combat Cybercrime: Investigations and Collaborations The FBI has dedicated significant resources to combatting cybercrime, including establishing specialized units and task forces. These efforts have led to numerous successful investigations and arrests of high-profile hackers. The FBI also collaborates with international partners, sharing intelligence and best practices to stay ahead of the evolving threat landscape. This cooperation enables us to disrupt criminal networks and bring perpetrators to justice. What You Can Do to Protect Yourself: Tips and Best Practices It's essential for individuals and organizations to take proactive measures to protect themselves from cyber threats. This includes implementing robust security protocols, keeping software up-to-date, and being cautious when interacting with unfamiliar links or attachments. The FBI also encourages the public to report any suspicious activity or potential cybercrimes to the appropriate authorities. NIST.Guru NIST Compliance Guide Welcome NIST NIST (National Institute of Standards & Technology) is part of the US Department of Commerce. Congress established the agency in 1901 to promote the US economy and public welfare by providing technical leadership for the nation’s measurement and standards infrastructure. NIST 800 - 171 NIST 800-171 was created in 2015 and it specifically covers the protection of “Controlled Unclassified Information” (CUI). CUI Controlled Unclassified Information is defined as information created by the government that is unclassified, but needs safeguarding. CUI is information that is sensitive and relevant to the interests of the United States, but not strictly regulated by the US government. NIST 800 - 53 Defines the standards and guidelines for federal agencies to architect and manage their information security systems. It was established to provide guidance for the protection of agency's and citizen's private data. Assessment Process Following the testing guidance from the National Institute of Standards and Technology (NIST), an assessment will be conducted to determine your company’s compliance with NIST 800-171. מתווה הצעירים של ישראל לשירות העם מתווה הצעירים של ישראל לשירות העם חרדים וחילונים מסרבים להיות אויבים! שם מלא טלפון מקום מגורים גיל שלח מתווה הצעירים של ישראל לשירות העם 1. כולנו אחים – הקריאה להגן על הבית ולשרת את עם ישראל מגיעה מתוך אהבה הדדית ואחריות משותפת להמשך קיומו של העם היהודי, תוך מציאת מכנה משותף רחב ככל האפשר לצד כבוד והבנה לדרכה הייחודית של כל קהילה, וכל זאת מתוך תחושת שותפות גורל עמוקה. 2. הכרה היסטורית בארגוני החסד החרדיים – המגזר החרדי משופע בארגוני חסד, והמדינה תכיר בתרומתם של הארגונים האלו. שירות בארגונים כמו זק"א ויד שרה הם חלק מתרומה לשותפות שלנו כעם, ויוגדרו כשירות אזרחי מוכר כשירות שווה ערך בזכויות ובחובות לשירות הלאומי. 3. כל אחד תורם לעם ללא יוצא מן הכלל – התהליך יהיה מתון, מדוד, ויכלול מסלולים מותאמים לכל קהילה. השותפות תיבנה בצורה מדודה ומתונה ותוך הכרה בכך שתהליכי עומק ושינויים משמעותיים מצריכים זמן והיערכות מתאימה. 4. לא תהיה פגיעה בלימוד התורה – מי שלומד תורה יוכל בהמשך חייו לקחת חלק במסלולים המוכרים. לימוד התורה הוא העוגן הרוחני המקיים את העם היהודי במשך אלפי שנות גלות עד עצם ימינו אלה, והקריאה לשוויון חובות וזכויות אין משמעה קריאה לפגיעה בלומדי התורה. 5. צה"ל יבצע התאמות וייערך לגיוס חרדים – צה"ל וארגונים נוספים הקיימים היום, יתאימו את עצמם לצרכים החרדיים וייערכו לקלוט את החרדים שאינם לומדים תורה, בצורה שלא נוגדת את הערכים החרדיים, ובצורה בה חרדים משרתים יוכלו לשמור על הצביון החרדי שלהם. הכל יוצאים למלחמה – אך כל שבט רשאי להשאר בייחודו. 2024 Ⓒ נבנה ע''י אלפא מדיה

ISACA Finland Chapter (Tietojärjestelmien tarkastus ja valvonta ry) on yhdistys, jonka toiminnan tarkoituksena on kehittää ja edistää hyvää tietohallintatapaa (IT Governance), tietojärjestelmätarkastusta, tietoturvallisuutta sekä IT-riskienhallintaa. ISACA Finland on kansainvälisen ISACA Internationalin Suomen jäsenjärjestö. ISACAssa on maailmanlaajuisesti jäseniä yli 110.000 ja Suomessa 550, jotka toimivat yrityselämän ja julkishallinnon palveluksessa muun muassa konsultoinnin, tietoturvan, tietotekniikan, tietohallinnon, riskienhallinnan, sisäisen tarkastuksen ja tilintarkastuksen tehtävissä. ISACA on mukana kansainvälisesti hyväksytyn IT Governance -viitekehyksen COBITin ja sentyökalujen kehittämisessä. ISACAn myöntämiä sertifikaatteja ovat CISA (Certified InformationSystems Auditor), CISM (Certified Information Security Manager), CGEIT (Certified in the Governance of Enterprise IT) sekä CRISC (Certified in Risk and Information Systems Control). ISACA Finland Chapter järjestää jäsenilleen kuukausittain jäsenkokouksia ja vuosittain useitamaksullisia kursseja sekä osallistuu alaan liittyvään yhteiskunnalliseen keskusteluun ja toimintaan. Youth Community Mapping YC Mapping: Showcase of Youth Community Mapping Projects Home Projects United States International Calendar Related Organizations Resources About Us Learn More FAQ Welcome to Youth Community Mapping Since 2004, when 4-H launched Youth Community Mapping at the 4-H Technology Conference in St. Louis Forest Park, 4-H clubs in more than 1,000 counties have launched efforts to assist youth teams to visualize and analyze environmental, social and economic conditions that need action. In many cases their efforts have resulted in corrective action by companies, organizations and public groups. Youth Community Mapping is an energetic group of adults who support and showcase Youth Community Mapping projects in the United States. Our team includes 4-H volunteers, retired technology workers, schoolteachers, and youth leaders. We invite you to click through the pages to see what talented youth have created. Mentored by caring adults, these youth have used GPS locators, GIS software, and data collection techniques to help their communities through a variety of projects. What is the ACHM? The ACHM has worked to develop an image of hyperbaric oxygen therapy as a distinct medical specialty, often requiring full time practice. The ACHM has served as a primary educational resource for providers practicing hyperbaric and wound medicine and has established training criteria and certification pathways for clinicians. About Us Education We are pleased to offer many HBOT educational opportunities. These courses have been approved by our Education Committee using our ACHM Education Approval Process. ACHM Members receive a discount on all courses we have endorsed, which all offer CME/CEU credit. A pathway to certification is also available. Education Become a Member Membership to the ACHM is for those in the medical community specializing in wound care or hyperbaric medicine in the United States. The ACHM strives to build upon the work of its members to improve the quality, practice, and expand the scope of hyperbaric medicine. We are proud to provide an international support network hyperbaric community. Membership “Joining a hyperbaric medicine society is not just a professional commitment; it’s a gateway to a community dedicated to advancing knowledge and expertise. In the collaborative space of such societies, practitioners unite, fostering a dynamic exchange of ideas and insights. Together, we elevate the standards of care, ensuring that every dive into the depths of hyperbaric medicine is guided by shared wisdom and a commitment to excellence.” Categories No categories Search Search for: Meta Log in Charity WordPress Theme By Themeshopy Scroll to Top

Feel free to reach via contact form. 290 Maryam Springs 260, Courbevoie, Paris Email: hello@liquid-themes.com Phone: +47 213 5941 295 Toggle navigation WHO WE ARE ACGM BOARD NEWS & EVENTS PARTNERSHIPS MEMBERSHIP Overview China-Ghana Mining Association (ACGM) Profile The Association of China-Ghana Mining (ACGM) unites major Chinese mining companies and mining services companies in Ghana to promote responsible mining, enhance industry cooperation, and support investment. ACGM fosters sustainability, technological exchange, and regulatory guidance for SMEs while strengthening China-Ghana communication and collaboration, contributing to Ghana’s economic, social, and environmental development through various initiatives. Key Functions Investment Facilitation : Channel Chinese capital into Ghana’s mining sector and enhance high-quality investment inflows. Technology Transfer : Introduce China’s advanced technologies in low-grade ore processing and underground mining to improve operational efficiency. Compliance Guidance : Support Chinese SMEs in ethical operations, emphasizing social responsibility and environmental stewardship. Knowledge Hub : Provide policy insights and market intelligence to aid informed decision-making. Capacity Building : Organize technical training and management exchanges to cultivate industry talent. Dispute Mediation : Assist in resolving legal and commercial conflicts to boost the integrity of the market. Structure ACGM comprises mining enterprises and service providers from both nations, governed by a Board of Directors and managed by a Secretariat. Prospects ACGM will continue to drive joint projects, integrate cutting-edge technologies, and promote green mining practices, ensuring a balance between economic growth, ecological protection, and social equity for mutual prosperity.
